cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about training neural sequence to sequence models using classical objective functions for structured prediction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves optimization and learning, which makes cs.LG (Learning) another likely category. The use of neural networks and deep learning techniques suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category. The paper also reports new state of the art results on summarization, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
